> - `docs/blip-procedural-sfx-exploration.md` — full design + pseudo-code + 20 concrete examples. §13 (locked decisions) + §14 (MVP scope) are ground truth.
> - `docs/blip-post-mvp-extensions.md` — scope boundary (what''s OUT of MVP).
