INSERT INTO public.ia_project_spec_journal VALUES (5, 'TECH-73', 'decision_log', '| Date | Decision | Rationale | Alternatives considered |
|------|----------|-----------|-------------------------|
| 2026-04-06 | **Issue id TECH-73** | Next free **TECH-** in open **BACKLOG** after **TECH-72** | — |
| 2026-04-06 | **Umbrella** tracks **analysis doc** phases | Single **Spec:** for charter; phased **Acceptance** | **TECH-73a/b/c** split before **Phase 1** — deferred |
| 2026-04-06 | **Phase 1** first **`kind`**: **`export_agent_context`** | **`ExportAgentContext()`** is public static, runs **Edit** + **Play**, tolerates missing **grid** per **unity-development-context** §10 — lowest friction vertical slice | **Sorting debug** first (**Play** + initialized **grid** for full output) — deferred |
| 2026-04-06 | **Phase 1** MCP: single tool **`unity_bridge_command`** | One schema to validate; **`kind`** enum expands later | Per-export MCP tools — **Phase 2** sugar if token cost warrants |
| 2026-04-06 | **Postgres-only** bridge: table **`agent_bridge_job`** (**`0008`**); **MCP** insert + poll; **Unity** **Node** dequeue/complete | Removes filesystem race and aligns with **Editor export registry**; **`unity_bridge_get`** for async reads | **`.agent-bridge/`** files — superseded |
| 2026-04-06 | **MCP** wait policy: blocking poll up to **`timeout_ms`** (default **5000**) | Fast failure when **Unity** idle; configurable upper bound | Return **`command_id`** immediately — partially addressed by **`unity_bridge_get`** |
