| 2026-04-06 | **Unity** hook: **`[InitializeOnLoadMethod]`** on static **`RegisterUpdate`** | Subscribes **`EditorApplication.update`** once per domain reload; avoids duplicate **`InitializeOnLoad`** class ctor patterns | Static ctor only — equivalent |', '{close,friction,territory-ia,cursor,unity,editor,play,mode,request,same,machine-readable,outputs,defined,unity-development-context,context,agents,agent,sorting,debug,cell,chunk,interchange,json,artifact,terrain_cell_chunk,world,snapshot,geography,init,report,inventory,read}', '.cursor/projects/TECH-73.md', '2026-04-06 19:51:52.640323-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
