INSERT INTO public.ia_project_spec_journal VALUES (57, 'TECH-248', 'decision_log', '| Date | Decision | Rationale | Alternatives considered |
|------|----------|-----------|------------------------|
| 2026-04-16 | Canonical URL form = comma-delimited single param after any toggle | Shorter URLs; single `key=` is simpler than repeated params for manual inspection | Always emit repeated params — rejected, verbose URLs |
| 2026-04-16 | Input parser accepts BOTH comma + repeated forms | External links / hand-typed URLs may arrive in either shape; round-trip tolerance | Reject repeated params — rejected, brittle |
| 2026-04-16 | Return sorted array from `parseFilterValues` | Deterministic for server-render cache + chip-rendering order stability | Insertion-order preservation — rejected, non-deterministic across redirects |
| 2026-04-16 | Duck-typed second arm `{ getAll }` instead of importing `ReadonlyURLSearchParams` | `ReadonlyURLSearchParams` lives in `next/navigation` (client-hook surface); importing into a pure RSC-safe module would pull in client bundle. Duck type preserves structural compatibility with client callers without the import. | Import `ReadonlyURLSearchParams` directly — rejected, breaks purity gate (Acceptance #4). Drop union arm — rejected, blocks future client caller ergonomics. |
| 2026-04-16 | Strip empty + whitespace-only tokens during parse | `?status=,Draft` + manual URL edits produce stray empty segments; silently filtering matches user intent. | Preserve raw tokens — rejected, pollutes chip render with blank chips. |
| 2026-04-16 | Smoke test as throwaway tsx file, not committed suite | `web/` has no Jest / Vitest runner; `validate:all` cannot execute unit tests. Throwaway tsx smoke gives confidence without adding a test-runner dependency mid-stage. | Add Vitest to `web/` — rejected, scope creep vs Stage 4.4 Exit. Skip smoke — rejected, regressions would surface only after TECH-249 wiring. |', '{author,pure,typescript,module,exposing,helpers,plus,constant,parsefiltervalues,params,string,accepts,comma-delimited,repeated,de-dupes,web/lib/dashboard/filter-params,returns,sorted,array,togglefilterparam,currentsearch,value,adds,removes,param,query,clearfiltershref,/dashboard,side-effect-free,consumable,page,future}', 'ia/projects/TECH-248.md', '2026-04-16 12:01:22.387086-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
