| 2026-04-16 (kickoff) | Scope trimmed to `Awake` mute-restore block only | `SfxMutedKey` const already landed alongside TECH-243 consumer to avoid compile-break ordering; re-adding would double-declare | Re-declare const + fail build — rejected |', '{extend,blipbootstrap,awake,read,playerprefs,getint,sfxmutedkey,clamp,-80f,blipmixer,setfloat,sfxvolumeparam,muted,cold-start,player,blipsfxmuted,hears,silence,first,blip,play,opening,options,satisfies,stage,exit,bullet,public,const,string,constant,reads}', 'ia/projects/TECH-245.md', '2026-04-16 14:17:24.699343-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
