| 2026-04-18 | Re-export `Status` from `plan-tree.ts` | Downstream `TreeNode.tsx` (Stage 7.2) imports union from one place; decouples from `BadgeChip` path churn | Import `Status` directly from `BadgeChip` everywhere — rejected, tighter coupling |
| 2026-04-18 | Empty stage/step → `''pending''` + zero counts | Matches existing metrics convention (no tasks = not started) | Null-propagate — rejected, leaks undefined into render |
| 2026-04-18 | Phase sort = lexicographic ascending on `task.phase` | Deterministic render order + matches existing parse.mjs phase-string convention | Numeric sort — rejected, phase field is string per `TaskRow.phase` |', '{pure,builder,buildplantree,plan,metrics,synthesizes,renderable,treenodedata,forest,step,stage,phase,task,nodes,synthesized,groupby,phases,checklist,distinct,concept,jsdoc,flags,divergence,per-node,status,badgechip,union,satisfies,exit,bullet,web/lib/plan-tree,ships}', 'ia/projects/TECH-342.md', '2026-04-18 06:37:17.89079-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
