| 2026-04-18 | `GetById(-1)` → null contract | Aligns with `Zone.subTypeId = -1` RCI sentinel (TECH-279) | Throw on negative (rejected — defensive null flows back through RCI path cleanly) |
| 2026-04-18 | Duplicate id policy = first-match wins | Minimal logic; collision check pushed to TECH-283 asserts | Throw on duplicate load (rejected — class-only scope, no asset yet) |', '{scriptableobject,class,zonesubtyperegistry,cataloging,zone,sub-types,police,fire,education,health,parks,public,housing,offices,fields,entry,displayname,prefab,basecost,monthlyupkeep,icon,getbyid,lookup,asset,seeding,lands,tech-281,date,decision,rationale,alternatives,considered}', 'ia/projects/TECH-280.md', '2026-04-18 07:22:00.89691-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
INSERT INTO public.ia_project_spec_journal VALUES (159, 'TECH-302', 'decision_log', '| Date | Decision | Rationale | Alternatives considered |
