| 2026-04-18 | Load from JSON via AddComponent, not AssetDatabase | Registry is now MonoBehaviour (TECH-280 alignment); JSON file in Resources is the source of truth; no SO asset path | AssetDatabase.LoadAssetAtPath (rejected — requires SO .asset, no longer applicable) |
| 2026-04-18 | Test `IsStateServiceZone` via instance `EconomyManager` | Predicate is instance method (not static) on `EconomyManager` MonoBehaviour; no `Awake`, `Start` has `FindObjectOfType` but does not fire in EditMode — safe to `AddComponent` in `[SetUp]` | Reflection over predicate (rejected — brittle); refactor to static (rejected — out of scope, risks caller churn) |
| 2026-04-17 | Asmdef pattern = mirror `Blip.Tests.EditMode` | Single ref to `TerritoryDeveloper.Game` + `TestAssemblies` opt ref — consistent w/ existing sibling asmdef | Extend root `TerritoryDeveloper.EditModeTests` asmdef (rejected — keeps Economy tests isolable per-bucket) |
| 2026-04-17 | `JsonUtility` for subTypeId round-trip | In-memory, no PlayMode, no scene | Prefab instantiation (rejected — heavier, EditMode unfriendly) |', '{test,class,zonesubtyperegistrytests,asmdef,covers,zonesubtyperegistry,getbyid,lookup,round-trip,seeded,entries,"null",semantics,economymanager,isstateservicezone,assets/tests/editmode/economy/,predicate,bool,table,across,full,25-value,zonetype,enum,zone,subtypeid,default,jsonutility,serialization,locks,stage,scaffolding}', 'ia/projects/TECH-283.md', '2026-04-18 08:52:33.911667-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
INSERT INTO public.ia_project_spec_journal VALUES (168, 'TECH-371', 'decision_log', '| Date | Decision | Rationale | Alternatives considered |
