| 2026-04-18 | Sidecar JSON, not inline TS const | Loadable + cacheable + diffable; same pattern as `glossary-graph-index.json` | Inline TS map (harder to diff, mixes data w/ code) |
| 2026-04-18 | Option B (split object: `{ invariants, guardrails }`) | Cleaner type discrimination for TECH-372 handler; matches master-plan prose "13 invariants + guardrails block"; guardrail `index` field enables O(1) lookup per kind | Option A flat array (simpler JSON but mixing kinds complicates handler type narrowing) |', '{author,json,sidecar,array,number,subsystem_tags,string,covering,invariants,guardrails,block,pure,data,file,feeds,tools/mcp-ia-server/data/invariants-tags,ia/rules/invariants,stage,structured,handler,adds,domain,filter,invariants_summary,mcp-lifecycle-tools-opus-4-7-audit,orchestrator,date,decision,rationale,alternatives,considered,------}', 'ia/projects/TECH-371.md', '2026-04-18 09:04:53.825895-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
INSERT INTO public.ia_project_spec_journal VALUES (169, 'TECH-371', 'lessons_learned', '- …', '{author,json,sidecar,array,number,subsystem_tags,string,covering,invariants,guardrails,block,pure,data,file,feeds,tools/mcp-ia-server/data/invariants-tags,ia/rules/invariants,stage,structured,handler,adds,domain,filter,invariants_summary,mcp-lifecycle-tools-opus-4-7-audit,orchestrator,date,decision,rationale,alternatives,considered,------}', 'ia/projects/TECH-371.md', '2026-04-18 09:04:53.902194-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
INSERT INTO public.ia_project_spec_journal VALUES (170, 'TECH-372', 'decision_log', '| Date | Decision | Rationale | Alternatives considered |
|------|----------|-----------|------------------------|
| 2026-04-18 | Substring match on `subsystem_tags` | Forgiving + matches glossary-discover ranking style | Exact tag match (brittle for synonyms) |
| 2026-04-18 | Load sidecar once at `registerInvariantsSummary`, cache in closure | Registry called once at server boot; avoids per-call fs read | Per-call read (re-parse cost); async lazy load (adds complexity) |
| 2026-04-18 | Drop `code_touches` + `body` from return shape | Sidecar does not supply them; invariants.md has no separate body beyond the numbered line | Scrape body from adjacent markdown (out of scope for T1.2.2) |
| 2026-04-18 | Filter both invariants + guardrails by same `domain` | Symmetry; guardrails mirror invariants semantically | Filter only invariants (half-answer) |', '{extend,load,tech-371,sidecar,json,shape,invariants,number,subsystem_tags,guardrails,index,accept,domain,string,filter,tools/mcp-ia-server/src/tools/invariants-summary,tools/mcp-ia-server/data/invariants-tags,param,substring,match,against,return,structured,description,title,markdown,side-channel,re-emits,filtered,bullet,block,prose-style}', 'ia/projects/TECH-372.md', '2026-04-18 09:19:34.664337-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
