| 2026-04-18 | Observe `PostError` via `GetQueueCount()` delta | `PostError` is plain void, no event to subscribe; queue-count is low-coupling + already public API | Subclass spy (fragile); reflection on private queue field (brittle) |
| 2026-04-18 | Glossary row forward-refs `ia/specs/economy-system.md#treasury-floor-clamp` + fallback to `docs/zone-s-economy-exploration.md §IP-3` | Matches sibling `envelope (budget sense)` pattern; spec #12 allows forward-ref placeholders | Inline full def in glossary (duplicates future spec); wait for Stage 3.3 (blocks TECH-383 closeout) |', '{locks,stage,behavior,against,regression,treasuryfloorclampservicetests,reuses,asmdef,covers,tryspend,happy,path,floor-clamp,block,canafford,assets/tests/editmode/economy/,boundary,spendmoney,delegation,adds,treasuryfloorclampservice,glossary,cross-referenced,forthcoming,ia/specs/economy-system,date,decision,rationale,alternatives,considered,------,----------}', 'ia/projects/TECH-383.md', '2026-04-18 13:17:51.130612-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
