| 2026-04-18 | Stage-filter fixture exercises 3 sub-cases (match w/ pending, match all-Done, absent heading) | Covers `null` branches in core w/o inflating fixture count | 3 separate fixtures — overkill |', '{author,tests,fixtures,master_plan_next_pending,tech-415,fixture,plans,mixed,status,column,values,cover,scenarios,first-,_pending_,wins,draft,top-of-table,stage,filter,respected,fully-,done,returns,"null",determinism,rerun,phase,date,decision,rationale,alternatives}', 'ia/projects/TECH-416.md', '2026-04-18 16:31:40.196561-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
