| 2026-04-18 | TECH-417 owns locate + next-pending catalog rows; T4.2.3 (Stage 4.2) covers `parent_plan_validate` + `backlog_list` filter extension docs only | Avoid double-filing when both stages drift; author rows at first opportunity (Stage 4.1) | Defer all catalog work to T4.2.3 — leaves Stage 4.1 tools undiscoverable between stages |', '{update,both,tool,descriptors,master_plan_locate,master_plan_next_pending,canonical,use-case,prose,schema-cache,restart,note,catalog,entries,stage,docs/mcp-ia-server,phase,polish,task,required,either,callable,agent-side,workflows,date,decision,rationale,alternatives,considered,------,----------,-----------}', 'ia/projects/TECH-417.md', '2026-04-18 16:37:40.915183-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
