| 2026-04-19 | No orphan specs flagged | `validate:dead-project-specs` exits 0; all `ia/projects/*.md` have matching yaml | N/A |', '{validate,dead-project-specs,frontmatter,tech-454,strips,parent_phase,gate,stage,phase,exit,orphan,stale,fields,schema,breakage,specs,date,decision,rationale,alternatives,considered,------,----------,-----------,------------------------,2026-04-19,accept,advisory-mode,warnings,unrelated,skill,files}', 'ia/projects/TECH-455.md', '2026-04-19 08:53:01.16052-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
