| D3 | Ship first of Theme 0 five (B7 → D1 → E1 → E2 → D3) | Cheapest win; unblocks measurement for remaining four | audit ship order |', '{debug_mcp_compute,mcpservers,territory-ia,json,flag,surfaces,per-tool,cold-start,compute,timings,stderr,stdio-safe,audit-confirmed,source,theme,docs/session-token-latency-audit-exploration,quick,ship,order,decision,rationale,----------,-----------,--------,unconditional,secondary,gate,audit,nb-2,output,volume,acceptable}', 'ia/projects/TECH-466.md', '2026-04-19 12:22:27.608217-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
INSERT INTO public.ia_project_spec_journal VALUES (243, 'TECH-467', 'decision_log', '| Date | Decision | Rationale | Alternatives considered |
