| 2026-04-19 | Delete outright (not conditional rewrite) | Exploration §Approach B locked delete variant; conditional logic adds complexity w/o proven lift | Conditional rewrite (branch ≠ main / last verify failed / HEAD ahead upstream) — rejected |
| 2026-04-19 | NB-3 drift sweep excludes `docs/` historical audits | `session-token-latency-*.md` + `ai-mechanics-audit-*.md` reference script name as historical prose (audit artefacts); rewriting them destroys the decision paper trail | Rewrite prose refs → rejected (history loss) |
| 2026-04-19 | Drop `Stop` key entirely if array empties | Minimal settings.json shape; avoid dangling empty array | Keep `"Stop": []` — rejected (noise) |', '{stop,hook,fires,unconditional,verification,reminder,every,session,pure,noise,destabilises,cache-suffix,eligibility,gate,function,tools/scripts/claude-hooks/verification-reminder,/verify-loop,enforce,policy,delete,entry,script,sourced,docs/session-token-latency-audit-exploration,theme-0,item,date,decision,rationale,alternatives,considered,------}', 'ia/projects/TECH-467.md', '2026-04-19 12:35:11.723692-04', NULL, DEFAULT);
