- `validate:dead-project-specs` passes (no orphan specs).
- `npm run validate:all` passes.
- Migration JSON M3 flipped to `done`.
- Phase 1 — Spec frontmatter fold + dead-spec validate.
- Phase 2 — YAML schema update + BACKLOG regen.', 'pending', 'ia/projects/lifecycle-refactor-master-plan.md', '2026-04-24 14:37:53.117283-04', '2026-04-24 17:36:40.664541-04');
INSERT INTO public.ia_stages VALUES ('lifecycle-refactor', '7.2', 'Wiring Layer / Agents + Commands + Rule Docs + Validation', 'Wire new skills into agent + command surface; author plan-author + subagent-progress-emit + stage-closeout pair; rewrite lifecycle rule docs; validate end-to-end. Full scope context: Stage 7.1 Objectives.', NULL, 'pending', 'ia/projects/lifecycle-refactor-master-plan.md', '2026-04-24 14:37:53.117283-04', '2026-04-24 17:36:40.674477-04');
